Class DataNodeConfigInfo

java.lang.Object
  org.apache.cayenne.project.DataNodeConfigInfo
Deprecated. since 3.0. ProjectConfigurator approach turned out to be not usable, and is in fact rarely used (if ever). It will be removed in subsequent releases. 

public class DataNodeConfigInfo
extends Object

Stores information necessary to reconfigure nodes of existing projects.
